title: Electronic Sampler Pack
description:
Alright, well my friend wanted to have a starting point for finding cool electronic artists so he asked me to make this...
I know it's not comprehensive, and it's lacking suspiciously from some genres (trance, dnb) and has more breakbeat stuff, and it's not that indepth, but that's not the point. i didn't upload this for anyone else, but if you enjoy it anyway thats great.
